le.\00\00\00\00\0aStalePrice\00\00\00\00\05z\00\00\00\15The price is too high\00\00\00\00\00\00\0cPriceTooHigh\00\00\05{\00\00\00\14The price is too low\00\00\00\0bPriceTooLow\00\00\00\05|\00\00\00GThe length of the arrays to create multiple statements is not the same.\00\00\00\00\17InconsistentInputLength\00\00\00\05\dd\00\00\00%The ID of the new statement is empty.\00\00\00\00\00\00\12InvalidStatementId\00\00\00\00\05\de\00\00\003There already exists a statement with the given ID.\00\00\00\00\18CannotOverwriteStatement\00\00\05\df\00\00\00\15The team ID is empty.\00\00\00\00\00\00\0dInvalidTeamId\00\00\00\00\00\05\e0\00\00\005The closing account balance is not greater than zero.\00\00\00\00\00\00\1cBalanceMustBeGreaterThanZero\00\00\05\e1\00\00\00+There is not a statement with the given ID.\00\00\00\00\11StatementNotFound\00\00\00\00\00\05\e2\00\00\00=The new closing account balance is less than the paid amount.\00\00\00\00\00\00\12BalanceAlreadyPaid\00\00\00\00\05\e3\00\00\00+The amount to pay is less or equal to zero.\00\00\00\00\0eAmountTooSmall\00\00\00\00\05\e4\00\00\00>The amount to pay exceeds the remaining debt of the statement.\00\00\00\00\00\0cAmountTooBig\00\00\05\e5\00\00\00/There are no assets to liquidate the statement.\00\00\00\00\08NoAssets\00\00\06A\00\00\00&The statement is not liquidatable yet.\00\00\00\00\00\13TooEarlyToLiquidate\00\00\00\06B\00\00\00\5cThe team ID of the statement does not match the team ID of the statement that is being paid.\00\00\00\0eTeamIdMismatch\00\00\00\00\06C\00\00\00\01\00\00\02RRepresents the structure to store the assets supported by the coordinator.\0a- `asset`: The address of the asset that is supported.\0a- `oracle`: The optional address of the oracle that is used to get the price of the asset. If\0anone, the asset is considered stable to dollar.\0a- `stale_threshold`: The optional number of seconds after which the price of the asset is\0aconsidered stale.\0a- `min_price`: The optional minimum price of the asset